{"data":[{"name":"87:1","price":"(1) Exalt the name of your Lord, the Most High,","arabic":"سَبِّحِ ٱسۡمَ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡأَعۡلَى","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5949,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"87:2","price":"(2) Who created and proportioned","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5950,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"87:3","price":"(3) And who destined and [then] guided","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِي قَدَّرَ فَهَدَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5951,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"87:4","price":"(4) And who brings out the pasture","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِيٓ أَخۡرَجَ ٱلۡمَرۡعَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5952,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"87:5","price":"(5) And [then] makes it black stubble.","arabic":"فَجَعَلَهُۥ غُثَآءً أَحۡوَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5953,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"87:6","price":"(6) We will make you recite, [O Muḥammad], and you will not forget,","arabic":"سَنُقۡرِئُكَ فَلَا تَنسَىٰٓ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5954,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"87:7","price":"(7) Except what Allāh should will. Indeed, He knows what is declared and what is hidden.","arabic":"إِلَّا مَا شَآءَ ٱللَّهُۚ إِنَّهُۥ يَعۡلَمُ ٱلۡجَهۡرَ وَمَا يَخۡفَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5955,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"87:8","price":"(8) And We will ease you toward ease.[1907]","arabic":"وَنُيَسِّرُكَ لِلۡيُسۡرَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5956,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1907]- To the path of Allāh's religion, which is easy and natural, or toward Paradise, by giving opportunities for righteous deeds.","lang":"en"},{"name":"87:9","price":"(9) So remind, if the reminder should benefit;[1908]","arabic":"فَذَكِّرۡ إِن نَّفَعَتِ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5957,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1908]- i.e., wherever it will be heard and understood.","lang":"en"},{"name":"87:10","price":"(10) He who fears [Allāh] will be reminded.","arabic":"سَيَذَّكَّرُ مَن يَخۡشَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5958,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"87:11","price":"(11) But the wretched one will avoid it –","arabic":"وَيَتَجَنَّبُهَا ٱلۡأَشۡقَى","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5959,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"87:12","price":"(12) [He] who will [enter and] burn in the greatest Fire,","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي يَصۡلَى ٱلنَّارَ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5960,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"87:13","price":"(13) Neither dying therein nor living.","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَا يَمُوتُ فِيهَا وَلَا يَحۡيَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5961,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"87:14","price":"(14) He has certainly succeeded who purifies himself","arabic":"قَدۡ أَفۡلَحَ مَن تَزَكَّىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5962,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"87:15","price":"(15) And mentions the name of his Lord and prays.","arabic":"وَذَكَرَ ٱسۡمَ رَبِّهِۦ فَصَلَّىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5963,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"87:16","price":"(16) But you prefer the worldly life,","arabic":"بَلۡ تُؤۡثِرُونَ ٱلۡحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5964,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"87:17","price":"(17) While the Hereafter is better and more enduring.","arabic":"وَٱلۡأٓخِرَةُ خَيۡرٞ وَأَبۡقَىٰٓ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5965,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"87:18","price":"(18) Indeed, this is in the former scriptures,","arabic":"إِنَّ هَٰذَا لَفِي ٱلصُّحُفِ ٱلۡأُولَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5966,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"87:19","price":"(19) The scriptures of Abraham and Moses.","arabic":"صُحُفِ إِبۡرَٰهِيمَ وَمُوسَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5967,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"}],"chapter":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la","Chapter Al-A'la","A'la","Surah A'la","Chapter A'la","Al A'la","Surah Al A'la","Chapter Al A'la","Surah 87","Chapter 87","The Most High","الأعلى"]}